high_descs: Walk into the kitchen to the counter along the wall, moving slightly to the left to avoid the counter next to the stove.  Turn right to face the stove top.
Pick up the skillet from the back right burner on the stove top.
Holding the skillet, turn right and walk to the fridge.

Open the fridge door (bottom door) and put the skillet inside the fridge on the shelf to the right of the egg.  Close the door, wait 7 seconds, then open the fridge (bottom) door again.  Take out the skillet that is to the right of the egg, and close the fridge door.
Holding the skillet, turn around 180 degrees, walk back to the counter and turn to face the stove top.
Put the skillet on the front right burner on the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled skillet on the front burner of the stove top.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight, and turn right, then turn right again to face the stove.
Pick up the pan from the right side of the stove.
Turn around, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the pan inside of the fridge.
Turn around, then turn right to face the stove.
Placed the pan on the front right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the stove.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the stove in front of you and turn to the right to face it.
Pick up the blue pan that is on the stove on the back burner on the right.
Turn to your right and walk across the room to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, place the pan on the shelf to the right of the mug and the egg, close the refrigerator door, open the door and remove the pan from the shelf and then close the door again.
Turn around, walk across the room to the stove, and turn right to face it.
Place the pan on the stove on the front burner on the right.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan from the back burner to the front burner.
